<h1 id="getting-familiarized-with-python">Getting familiarized with Python</h1>

<p>Note that Python is simpler than you would expect. Once you get to know of the basic syntax, you can start writing complicated code. Understand the following to begin with:</p>
<ul>
  <li>How to assign a value to a variable.</li>
  <li>How to handle a list (only the basics).</li>
  <li>How to use a for loop.</li>
  <li>It is fun to use random function. Try simulating a coin toss.</li>
</ul>

